{"type": "article", "id": 59202, "title": "变身剪刀的仙人掌，也是你的桌面小摆饰｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-12-11T22:52:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52312, "name": "EMKO"}, {"id": 54997, "name": "Comité de Proyectos"}, {"id": 54998, "name": "TSATSAS"}, {"id": 54893, "name": "Qualy Design"}, {"id": 54999, "name": "Silvia Ceñal"}, {"id": 55000, "name": "Ming Liu"}, {"id": 55001, "name": "Dieter Rams"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181211194541tEcIj4wuGnoQS0Yp.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Cactus Scissors by Qualy Design</h3><p>泰国新锐设计品牌 Qualy Design 的产品都是将设计融于各种令人会心一笑的妙趣之中。比如这款变身剪刀的仙人掌，期待为你的居家生活增添更多的绿意与趣味。</p><p>“仙人掌”除了有剪刀功能外，盆栽处还能转开，收纳你的杂乱小物，让你的办公桌不再凌乱，也能成为你桌面的独特摆饰。售价 24 美元，<a href=\"http://inter.qualydesignstore.com/product/cactus/?v=cb21c4d7dea9\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194651qBuoeJbOUPYZ4FfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194651fNsQVLun1HRFaB02.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194651jQnwUumA097rsFpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194652GVdhMO7meDqWZwYb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194652DVJIzbLxMOZQwXEU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194652A7SMqsIKUk4dCnf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812111946533L1w9ujBJ0UnosCD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>931 handbag by TSATSAS</h3><p>提到设计师 Dieter Rams ，你可能会想到他在博朗的产品或者 Vitsœ 家具，但你知道他在 1963 年设计过一款手提包吗？</p><p>当时，Dieter Rams 为他的妻子，Ingeborg 设计了一个皮革手提包 931，制造商是德国品牌 TSATSAS。这款名为 931 的手提包给人一种经典的感觉，就像他的其他产品一样，剔除掉一切冗余装饰，符合他“少即是多”的设计原则。</p><p>这款手工制作的包包采用黑色或灰色小牛皮制成，饰有蓝色羊羔皮纳帕内饰，内有各种隔层，保持物品整齐收纳。</p><p>直到今年，TSATSAS 为这款手提包加入并改进了一些细节，以使其更具功能性，并将其重新推向市场。售价 900 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.tsatsas.com/collection_931_dieter_rams.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194818uUXgj0iQWxPksEG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194818gneAtfxS0hkGcYNF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194818K8Fs0auG2TrVtoLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194819gZYftEm6uzqex5oS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194819C03PfAkZKVLEyXF4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194819XCE53Gp7v2WgBsSK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194819np0kPNVxlAB7zXKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194819ZYe1dNbMyKzVECgm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194820k5hDqjPnZGXi0bJm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>A Stable Bookcase by  Comité de Proyectos </h3><p>去年，墨西哥经历了毁灭性的地震，引发了墨西哥城设计工作室 Comité de Proyectos 关于安全性和稳定性的更多思考。</p><p>他们决定重新考虑使用 Librero Entropía 或 Bookcase Entropy 的普通书架，这些书架使用通常不用于货架设计的固体材料，书柜由坚实的白橡木、金属和铸造混凝土组成，它们组合在一起形成一个独特而坚固的结构，可以放置用户的书籍、小摆设和植物。</p><p>木质搁板由铸造混凝土件支撑，确保搁板不会移动到任何地方。除了混凝土支撑外，它们还包含三个垂直金属立管，不仅可以帮助搁置搁板，还可以提供与较重的混凝土件形成鲜明对比的视觉体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194855Hq6zhjgpMtL0R18o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194855sIg9Z8a0zAPYxmol.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194856rUOlW4BZdwQDNSvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194856w9gzJKNxUp6rYFZc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194856gcRF6ZhUKit1k9O0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194857MEK3cZOvJbYdDqF4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.comitedeproyectos.mx/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Comité de Proyectos</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>IRONING Hair Dryer by Ming Liu</h3><p>不管是出差还是旅行，有限的行李箱空间很有可能需要你在很多日常物品中作出取舍，比如吹风机和熨斗。尤其是遇到要去参加商务会议的场合，我们都希望衣服看起来漂亮整洁，头发蓬松柔软。</p><p>最近，设计师 Ming Liu 推出了一款熨烫吹风机，外形近似于传统吹风机，采用直观的折叠方式，可以放入行李箱。</p><p>但是，位于手柄底部的是储水器，可以利用热空气使其成为蒸汽。当附件定位在喷嘴上时，产品会变成熨斗。对于经常出差或是旅行的人来说，这绝对是一个有价值的产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194956oGvbn85PyH0jqQY2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194956L40EkWGlSuFovdfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194956TlIzNEj87bihpJGd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812111949578hy57m2OGX0rT9xE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194957hsLdI49Rb3ZTuHC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194957InCvgrQqaWpmVMDy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194957ZkI18l7oMp2sQaWf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194957Q82KTSR9dcpMVCFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211194958vSeH7ikFsjKTzDOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/12/07/a-handy-product-for-busy-travellers/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Macaron Floor Lamp by Silvia Ceñal for EMKO</h3><p>几年前，西班牙设计师 Silvia Ceñal 推出了 Macaron 落地灯的原型设计，最近立陶宛公司 EMKO 决定量产它。</p><p>它看起来有点像是一款吊灯，像一款可爱的马卡龙，搭配简单的材料，比如木头和伸缩，恰当的比例，渲染出活泼的个性。木制框架带来温暖的感觉，而螺纹线则通过颜色和纹理增添俏皮感。</p><p>目前，Macaron 落地灯有两种尺寸和五种颜色可供选择，包括黑色、白色、蓝色、红色和黄色，售价 362 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.emko-online.lt/en/product-category/lighting/macaron-floor-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812111950475RY98SIpiw6ONTC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211195047FKzDc6xBQtNl0be1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211195047cOptigCS2bQJGvxM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211195047Wuhz5IxV6gfnCwRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181211195048FjoH8EyI1s6JmrpK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}